#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[*virt-manager*](http://virt-manager.org/) is a free software virtualization "
"solution for Linux. *virt-manager* has a more complex interface than "
"*VirtualBox* or *GNOME Boxes* but it also has a more complete set of "
"features."
